# Judging Rubric — Vibe Coding: AI Dream-to-App

Each judge rates 0–10 in each category. Weights convert to final score (out of 100).

1. Technical Implementation (30%) — correctness, stability, API use, DB usage.
2. Impact & Usefulness (25%) — real user value.
3. UX / Design (20%) — usability and polish.
4. Creativity & Innovation (15%) — unique use of AI.
5. Presentation & Demo (10%) — clarity and demo completeness.

Total = (Tech*0.30 + Impact*0.25 + UX*0.20 + Creativity*0.15 + Presentation*0.10) * 10
